ActIndian Act
SubjectTransfer of lands in Williams Lake Indian Reserve No.1, Five Mile Indian Reserve No.3 James Louie Indian Reserve No.3A and Carpenter Mountain Indian Reserve No.15, British Columbia
PrecisOrder (1) consenting to the exercise of the power of the Province of British Columbia to take administration and control of 13.64 hectares (33.71 acres) of land in WILLIAMS LAKE INDIAN RESERVE No.1, FIVE MILE INDIAN RESERVE No.3 JAMES LOUIE INDIAN RESERVE No.3A and CARPENTER MOUNTAIN INDIAN RESERVE No.15 (the lands); and (2) authorizing, in lieu of such taking, the transfer of administration and control of the required lands.
